1. Moj *prisustv* o na sastanku bio je neophodan. (My *presence* at the meeting was necessary.)
2. Ono što mi najviše nedostaje jeste *prisustvo* moje majke. (What I miss the most is the *presence* of my mother.)
3. Ako neko želi da učestvuje u diskusiji, molimo ga da pokaže svoje *prisustvo*. (If someone wants to participate in the discussion, please show your *presence*.)
4. Prijavila sam *prisustv* o na seminaru o marketingu. (I registered my *attendance* for the marketing seminar.)
5. Njegovo *prisustv* o u sobi nije primećeno dok nije počeo da govori. (His *presence* in the room wasn't noticed until he started speaking.)
6. Profesorica nam je ukazala na važnost *prisustva* na časovima. (The teacher pointed out the importance of *attendance* in class.)
7. *Prisustvo* druge osobe ponekad može biti dovoljno da se osetimo manje usamljeni. (The *presence* of another person can sometimes be enough to make us feel less lonely.)
8. Ako ne budete imali *prisustv* o duha, nećete moći da se suočite sa ovom situacijom. (If you don't have a *presence* of mind, you won't be able to deal with this situation.)